	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Here are the instructions to make both CIC enable/disable switch, and PAL/NTSC switch. <a href="http://mmmonkey.co.uk/console/nintendo/snes-switches-1.htm" class="postlink">http://mmmonkey.co.uk/console/nintendo/snes-switches-1.htm</a>
<br />
<br />Basically it's just grounding some pins on CIC and both PPUs.
<br />
<br />Most NTSC games will work on PAL SNES as long as PPUs work in NTSC mode.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


